main event: A civilian reported seeing one unidentified object in the sky over Waldport, Oregon on August 4, 1965.
interesting points: The observation lasted only 1.5 seconds,The document is a part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings,The report concluded there was insufficient data to classify the sighting,The object was not visually followed, indicating a sudden appearance,The report contained a request for additional information to assist in evaluation.
